 &lt;p&gt;⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://leetcode.com/problems/out-of-boundary-paths/description/?envType=daily-question&amp;amp;envId=2024-01-26&#34;&gt;&lt;ins class=&#34;dot&#34;&gt;題目敘述&lt;/ins&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There is an  &lt;code&gt;m x n&lt;/code&gt;  grid with a ball. The ball is initially at the position  &lt;code&gt;[startRow, startColumn]&lt;/code&gt; . You are allowed to move the ball to one of the four adjacent cells in the grid (possibly out of the grid crossing the grid boundary). You can apply &lt;strong&gt;at most&lt;/strong&gt;  &lt;code&gt;maxMove&lt;/code&gt;  moves to the ball.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Given the five integers  &lt;code&gt;m&lt;/code&gt; ,  &lt;code&gt;n&lt;/code&gt; ,  &lt;code&gt;maxMove&lt;/code&gt; ,  &lt;code&gt;startRow&lt;/code&gt; ,  &lt;code&gt;startColumn&lt;/code&gt; , return the number of paths to move the ball out of the grid boundary. Since the answer can be very large, return it &lt;strong&gt;modulo&lt;/strong&gt;  &lt;code&gt;10^9 + 7&lt;/code&gt; .&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;example-1&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#example-1&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Example 1&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://assets.leetcode.com/uploads/2021/04/28/out_of_boundary_paths_1.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Input:&lt;/strong&gt; m = 2, n = 2, maxMove = 2, startRow = 0, startColumn = 0&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Output:&lt;/strong&gt; 6&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;example-2&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#example-2&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Example 2&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://assets.leetcode.com/uploads/2021/04/28/out_of_boundary_paths_2.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Input:&lt;/strong&gt; m = 1, n = 3, maxMove = 3, startRow = 0, startColumn = 1&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Output:&lt;/strong&gt; 12&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;解題思路&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#解題思路&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 解題思路&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;solution&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#solution&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Solution&lt;/h2&gt;
